resource.name: Rail Station Footprints
resource.description:
Station envelope footprints for the 21 HHCTCP stations from East Kapolei to Ala Moana Center as presented in preliminary engineering (PE) drawings prepared for RTD/HART by Parsons Brinckerhoff and subconsultants in 2009/2010. These footrpints were traced in ArcMap over rubber-sheeted PE station area, architectural, and civil site plan drawings, and are not intended to be exact.
To be used principally for station area land use planning.
